      "beast_baseline": "i'm getting a bit confused with the analogies. can you just stick to the science for a second? if the iron and manganese are \"tied up,\" how do i actually tell the difference between that and a nitrogen deficiency without a lab test? is there anything i can do to the soil right now to help?",
